                            Anonymous
                            <span class="pull-right">10 days ago</span>
                            <p>There are conflicting accounts in the reviews on whether the Collector's CD-ROM version (1994) is included. I was even more uncertain since the product description explicitly states it includes "X-Wing Collector's CD-ROM... 1994". Well, I took a $10 shot and verified it: it does NOT include the 1994 version as advertised. Only the 1993 original and the 1998 remake. What a buzzkill! I'm sure the 1998 version is ok, but it doesn't have iMUSE and forces you to use a joystick, whereas with 1993 you lose the graphics advantages that came with the Collector's CD-ROM. Call me Goldilocks but you could have nailed it by including the 1994 version</p>
